Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like doing this to the elderly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're important witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you dying or running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've barricaded the back door and most\Nof the windows with furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it wouldn't be hard to\Nbreak in if they were serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's go down to the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use a gun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anything happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to live through this and tell the world the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in the room, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to you, Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a strong ally coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He comes to help me whenever\Nand wherever I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't forgive evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:03.87,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(259,200)\pos(373,363)}The Magnificent Steiner's Rage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head north through the woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think most of the children have escaped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry and get out of here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't checked the town center yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's one thing I have to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, do you know a person named Klaus Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the owner of Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I ran as fast as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the town is full of dead bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where to run to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's giving orders from his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange how he kept\Ncoming and going from the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he changed his clothes every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took a shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in a room on the fourth floor of Hotel Bergbach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he was like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is hiding in the other hotel, Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it there by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My journey of the imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has finally become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you here, reality finally makes an appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my vacation of following imaginary\Nthreads comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I have a duty as a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this girl with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you're after is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk after I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is unfolding in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the deepest part of my subconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the deepest part of your subconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to remember it, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Johan recalled this memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Johan already remembered it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm from this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the man giving orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you where Roberto is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are dead bodies everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go crazy if I stay in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to get to Hotel\NVersteck as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open your eyes, Erika
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your wife, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, your wife is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry and get to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna shoot the guy who killed Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Give me the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill the bastard who ruined our happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife doesn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife wishes for the safety of that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an escape route to the north through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about going to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to the forest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go anywhere anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about their target...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure they're not after the\Nmoney we won in the lottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't even feel alive these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, there was something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all that money, I even bought several guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal life really is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell my wife that it wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hennich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hennich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're shooting from the building across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this hotel have a basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a storage room under the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone crazy because he ran out\Nof alcohol, so he's doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how he hits me every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think your dad is someone\Nwho would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be over if I go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you die, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say something like that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tie you up down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm in trouble, the Magnificent Steiner shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a case like that during an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By applying excessive amounts of anger or sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a great deal of stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,another personality would arise within the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children had a bizarre violent nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most of them committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you lived to this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to you, just for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're from old East Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the former secret police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a nobody, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not under orders, but with your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask your hearts what it is you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came all the way here by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.96,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.00,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.92,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sitting in front of the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was glued to the television\Nfor that show every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.13,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what adventure awaits us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was glued to the television\Nfor that show every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:33.28,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in trouble, just call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall ever watching the last episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:33.80,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that weak young main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,knew that he turned into the Magnificent\NSteiner when he became filled with rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that young man became happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,became happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further and we'll be out of the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're residents of Ruhenheim, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is happening to the town, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people armed with weapons appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the town became a slaughterhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me you're with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen an Asian man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese man with black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you friends of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried his best to help these children escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stayed behind to continue helping the people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we left, he said he was going to the Hotel Versteck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've parked my car right outside the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive the injured and the sick away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and call the police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you planning on going into town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Asian man is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Versteck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people in the next building...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one on the floor below...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and another here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took out a total of four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner appeared, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything because I was engulfed in rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should treat that wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he found it in the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to Hotel Bergbach by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to treat you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure has been raining a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is nice when it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's sunny again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's take Wim here along with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and go on a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With delicious wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sad because I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad because my child is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for humans to forget their emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just lost somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a letter that was sent to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has finally reached me, decades later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is true sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last episode of the Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he returned to being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
